stateDiagram-v2
  [*] --> RECEIVED
  RECEIVED --> PROCESSED: validated and normalized
  PROCESSED --> APPROVAL_REQUIRED: policy threshold met
  PROCESSED --> SETTLEMENT_READY: no approval required
  APPROVAL_REQUIRED --> SETTLEMENT_READY: approved callback
  APPROVAL_REQUIRED --> REJECTED: rejected callback
  SETTLEMENT_READY --> SETTLED: settlement batch
  SETTLED --> [*]
  REJECTED --> [*]

